       [{"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "rewrite!"}]]},
        {"text": " is like "},
        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "rewrite"}]]},
        {"text": ","},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "but can also insert casts to adjust types that depend on the LHS of a rewrite."},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "It is available as an ordinary tactic and a "},
